{"tid":1820660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人！下一步！","createTime":"2020-01-11T15:48:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T03:22:36.000Z","uid":171633,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"10cb07a76502122ff178f78db4277c2914b05671","tid":1820660,"uid":171633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T15:48:10.000Z","msg":"呢排見到行動post愈來愈買少見少<br />\n遊行集會既抗爭手法亦都代價愈黎愈大<br />\n係國際上雖然有一班人仍然留意住香港動向<br />\n但不得不承認呢件事所引起既國際關注無一開始咁大<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以我哋要諗下其他方向！<br />\n<br />\n既然我哋知道黃色經濟圈係中共春袋 <br />\n咁我哋就更應該發大佢！<br />\n<br />\n簡單黎講就係將佢國際化<br />\n之前外國人話明白我哋處境但唔知可以用咩行動支持我哋<br />\n<br />\n所以，以後我哋集會遊行叫口號個陣加多句[/size=4]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>STAND WITH HONG KONG<br />\nBOYCOOT CHINA</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n[size=4]另外，無論係賺物上、旅行上，總之係一切生活都盡量向中國勢力說不！<br />\n<br />\n呢個都可以係Twitter 文宣既大方向<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yPLffMo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyPLffMo.png&h=127743c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A2tc2rp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA2tc2rp.png&h=63c99051&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">可以用呢排好興既meme 整圖po上twitter <br />\n提醒大家唔好買中國貨！ 杯葛中國</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"a1d3df772d2e58a4e3994a3e66d9a9347a3a37a9","tid":1820660,"uid":171633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T15:48:26.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"e38f3c4917c71277e79d074a1bcb19c50aae84a8","tid":1820660,"uid":171633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T15:48:36.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"013953f15b7d3d1202a5f7da33126ad6dac40d83","tid":1820660,"uid":171633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T15:48:47.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"d948d9bf22e532b3f7535b3b9feb8ef670314f31","tid":1820660,"uid":181789,"like":0,